creator: Asociety Corp.
descriptionHtml:
Go for the K.O.!
Make Your Opponent See Stars! Smash him!

Hey Noob! Maybe this game it's not for you! Are you ready to be at the top of the Multiplayer World League?

Find your own fighting game style in the Smash Boxing, new free mobile boxing arcade!

To be a champion you have to believe in yourself when no one else will ! Take a challenge and step on the ring to fight serious opponents ! Earn money, train and customize your fighter to make your way to the top!

CHALLENGE THE ROCKSTARS IN SINGLE PLAYER!

Your favorite Rock Stars Game are waiting to smash faces!
Be the challenger, fight your way through powerful opponents to win strongest champion.
Remember one thing - a champion is someone who gets up when he can’t!

MULTIPLAYER EXPERIENCE

Fight to opponents arround the world and promote to the best World Leagues! Don't forget to customize your player to show your style!

REAL BOXING MECHANICS

Punch, hook, uppercut, block and weave to make your way to the top! Deliver brutal knockout punches and win!

CUSTOMIZE YOUR FIGHTER

From boots and gloves to tattoo, hairstyle, etc- everything is customizable! Improve your skills, learn powerful Smash Punchs, use new equipment.

EASY CONTROLS

Tap and slide to place punches, hooks and perform devastating uppercuts. Use onscreen buttons to block and weave.

NOT PAY TO WIN

Just not.

If you like fighting game, with a touch of humor, easy to play, hard to master, cool graphics style, single and multiplayer... that's your game!
